{
  "stem": "7860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I became so prosperous on the train selling candy charms, because I used to sell my candy charms at night when the other boys were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when the time-- the activity for the black marketeers was at night, naturally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I didn't have no competition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day I became so greedy, I invaded some other boy's territory on another train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had never been there before in that direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the boys told me, that's-- that's our railroad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's our train, to get off, not to [INAUDIBLE] selling candy charms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't listen to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They bank robbed me, took everything away from me, and beat me up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to go again, singing songs and begging.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went back in business little by little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I slept wherever I could and whenever I could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to ride the train, let's say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the train was full of people at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people standing next to each other, body to body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you imagine me standing next to between those people, and lice infested?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to sleep by standing up next to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I slept also from 12 o'clock train until 4 o'clock in the morning behind that bookcase underneath the radiator there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Almost every night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I improvised a way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Otwock in the railroad station-- Otwock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Christmas time is a very, very-- every time Christmas comes around, it's very emotional to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Christmas day, the peasants are baking goodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Erev yontif they are preparing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're very generous and very charitable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Catholic religion is very similar, as far as charity is concerned, as the Jewish religion-- tzedakah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they are very generous, and they bake.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
